## Commercial License

Commercial licenses are available from McQuillen Interactive Pty. Ltd.

### License Tiers

| Tier           | Description                                                                                            |
| -------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Pro**        | For teams. Removes AGPL obligations, adds multi-org support, advanced analytics, and priority support. |
| **Enterprise** | For organisations. All Pro features plus SSO/LDAP, guest management, and dedicated support.            |

### Purchasing

Visit [https://validibot.com/pricing](https://validibot.com/pricing) for current pricing and to purchase a license.

Commercial licenses are provided as separate Python packages (`validibot-pro`, `validibot-enterprise`) distributed through a private package index after purchase.

### Commercial License Terms

Commercial licenses are governed by the Validibot Commercial License Agreement. Key terms include:

- **Subscription**: Licenses are annual subscriptions that must be renewed to continue use
- **Scope**: Licenses are per-organisation and non-transferable
- **Support**: Commercial licenses include support as specified in your subscription tier
- **No Warranty**: Software is provided "as is" without warranties
- **Liability Cap**: Our liability is limited to fees paid in the 12 months preceding any claim

See the full Commercial License Agreement provided with your purchase for complete terms.

