## Your Infrastructure, Your Responsibility

Validibot is designed for deployment on your own infrastructure.
McQuillen Interactive Pty. Ltd. does not host, operate, or have access to any
installation of the Software or any data you process.

**You are solely responsible for:**

- The security, availability, and operation of your infrastructure
- Backup, disaster recovery, and business continuity
- Applying security patches and updates
- Proper configuration and hardening
- Compliance with applicable data protection and privacy laws
- All data processed, stored, or transmitted through your installation

We accept no responsibility or liability for any data you process using this
Software or for security incidents arising from your infrastructure or
configuration.

